I’ve updated `MapInner` so the departure and arrival points are always fully inside the visible map, with padding around them.

Key change in `app/components/mapInner.tsx`:

```21:40:app/components/mapInner.tsx
  const bounds = L.latLngBounds(positions);

  return (
    <div className="w-full h-[400px] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg bg-[#e6f3ff]">
      <MapContainer
        bounds={bounds}
        boundsOptions={{ padding: [48, 48] }}
        style={{ height: "100%", width: "100%" }}
