#### 3) Map overlay: animated “sun” marker along the path

In `mapInner.tsx` I turned it into a client component and added a simple animation that moves a sun marker along the sampled positions:

```1:10:app/components/mapInner.tsx
"use client";

import { useEffect, useState } from "react";
import {
  MapContainer,
